title: Track Aircraft with a $20 Software Defined Radio
description:
Track Aircraft with a $20 Software Defined Radio


Tracking Aircraft with a $20 dongle and Software Defined Radio. Sniffing 1090 MHz for ADS-B to map live air traffic with free software. Plus, USB micro controller hacking with Richard Harmon at Shmoocon 2014
